info.author: Brian Ramos
info.description: PyZenity is an easy to use interface to Zenity for Python.  Zenity is normally called from scripts by invoking it with a multitude of command line parameters that it uses to construct its interfaces.  This module hides the details of invoking the command and presents simple API functions.
info.name: PyZenity
info.summary: An easy to use frontend to Zenity
